Description: Body sherd of black-figured North Ionian pottery plate; top, white slip; part of a tondo composition with a couch (?) with a cushion (?) on it, and possibly part of a table underneath; traces of added red and white on couch; on right, part of uncertain object (floral?) with added red and white; underside lightly ridged; worn brown-fired band.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GG.813)
